Description:
    List all available Rails commands with their options and metadata.

    This command is designed for programmatic consumption by tools and AI agents,
    providing structured output about available commands.

Examples:
    # Output all commands as a table (default)
    bin/rails commands

    # Output as JSON for programmatic consumption
    bin/rails commands --format=json

    # Output as YAML
    bin/rails commands --format=yaml

    # Filter commands by name pattern
    bin/rails commands --grep=db
    bin/rails commands -g migrate

    # Output only command names (minimal tokens)
    bin/rails commands --names-only --format=json

    # Combine grep and names-only for minimal output
    bin/rails commands --grep=db --names-only --format=json

    # Include hidden commands and help subcommands
    bin/rails commands --all

    # Exclude Rake tasks (Thor commands only)
    bin/rails commands --no-rake

Options:
    --format, -f     Output format: json, yaml, or table (default: table)
    --grep, -g       Filter commands by name (case-insensitive substring match)
    --names-only     Output only command names as a list
    --all            Include hidden commands and help subcommands
    --no-rake        Exclude Rake tasks

Output Schema (JSON):
    {
      "schema_version": "1.0",
      "rails_version": "8.0.0",
      "commands": [
        {
          "kind": "thor",
          "full_name": "routes",
          "namespace": "rails:routes",
          "command": "routes",
          "description": "List all the defined routes",
          "options": [
            {
              "name": "--controller",
              "aliases": ["-c"],
              "type": "string",
              "description": "Filter by a specific controller"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "rake",
          "full_name": "db:migrate",
          "namespace": "rake",
          "description": "Migrate the database",
          "arguments": ["version"]
        }
      ]
    }

Names-Only Output (JSON):
    ["about", "console", "db:migrate", "routes", "server", ...]
